Hell In A Bucket, Sugaree, Me & My Uncle-> Mexicali Blues, Brown Eyed Women, When I Paint My Masterpiece, Ramble On Rose, Let It Grow

reviews.review_text: Fair To Average Show Highlights: Hell In A Bucket
Check it out  Average first set...highlights are pre drums second set....Scarlet>Fire one of the best of the 80s, ripping Samson and well played Terrapin...post drums is decent
